Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,コードギアス反逆のルルーシュR2 TURN 23　シュナイゼル　の　仮面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,TURN 23　シュナイゼル　の　仮面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,神聖ブリタニア帝国?本土
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,フレイヤ弾頭による巨大な穴が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシィたちの人質になった各国代表
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,天子をだきしめる神楽耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,兵士たちの噂話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,といって倒れる咲世子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ナナリーと会話するルルーシュたち
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とシュナイゼル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,銃弾が放たれ 撃たれるコーネリア
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そばにつきそうジェレミアに事情を話します
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ベッドにこしかけるルルーシュ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュの手に自分の手をかさねるC.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,コンピューターにむかうニーナとロイドさん セシル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,前にでてきた鎮魂のローソク
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,決意をかためて歩くルルーシュ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,戦争の準備は着々と
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,中華連邦で演説するシンクーはあいかわらず血をはいているようで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,日本では 人々を前に玉城がはりきっています
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,水無瀬たち
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂さんを見て顔をあからめる千葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おなかをおさえるヴィレッタと扇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ラクシャータ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,カレンとジノ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,神楽耶と天子がうつります
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,扇に伝えるシンクー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アヴァロンに衝撃がつたわり
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,天子をだきしめる神楽耶の目に涙がうかんでいます
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お腹に赤ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,回想おわり
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy Britannian Empire - Homeland
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.79,0:00:07.36,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,て 帝都ペンドラゴンが消滅した？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The... The capital Pendragon's been annihilated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:08.59,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本当か？それは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.79,0:00:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:09.74,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,フレイヤ弾頭らしい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it was\Na F.L.E.I.J.A. warhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.79,0:00:11.86,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,トウキョウ租界を壊滅させた？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing that wiped out\Nthe Tokyo settlement?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:12.90,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,事故か？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:16.04,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しかし 製造したはずのフレイヤはなくなっていると
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.23,0:00:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've heard all the F.L.E.I.J.A. s\Nthey manufactured are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:18.19,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,軽挙妄動は慎め
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop spreading wild stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.73,0:00:20.37,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,帝都が消滅だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's just rumors, it's imprudent\Nto discuss the capital's destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:22.47,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,噂話だとしても不謹慎である
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:25.90,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいえ おそらく本当のことです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm afraid it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.95,0:00:28.63,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何っ？あっ　君は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.68,0:00:31.68,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュ様にお取次ぎ　を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...\NTake me to Master Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sekai no owari de\NAt the end of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Umareta hikari\NThe light that's born
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.01,0:00:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ima kaze no naka\NNow blows in the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kireigoto dake jaa ikirenai\NPretty words alone won't sustain you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasashisa dake jaa iyasenai\NKindness alone won't heal you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.28,0:01:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ubawareta nowa nanda\NWhat is it that was stolen from you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawaranai sekai de\NIn this unchanging world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikoetekita nowa nanda\NWhat is it that you hear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.46,0:01:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikisai no uta\NA song of color
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kudakechitta yume wo\NLet our crumbled dreams resound
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.13,0:01:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Asu no hate ni hibikaseru you ni\NAt the edge of tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sekai no owari de\NAt the end of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.88,0:01:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Umareta hikari\NThe light that's born
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bokura hitotsu ni\NBecomes one with us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.22,0:01:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ima kaze no naka\NNow blows in the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,SCHNEIZEL'S GUISE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:16.45,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ナ　ナナリー生きて　いたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.34,0:02:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nunnally... You're still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:19.36,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はいシュナイゼル兄様のおかげで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Yes, thanks to Brother Schneizel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.09,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,シュナイゼル？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Schneizel...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:25.34,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ナナリー 君はシュナイゼルが何をしたのかわかっているのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nunnally... Do you understand\Nwhat Schneizel has done?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:29.80,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい帝都ペンドラゴンにフレイヤ弾頭を撃ち込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Yes. He's attacked the capital,{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Pendragon, with a F.L.E.I.J.A. warhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.98,0:02:31.84,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それがわかっていてなぜ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know that,\Nthen why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.89,0:02:34.72,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,では　ギアスの方が正しいというのですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Are you saying using{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Geass is better?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:38.23,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お兄様もスザクさんも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You and big brother have been\Nlying to me all along, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:41.09,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと私に嘘をついていたのですね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:43.63,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本当のことをずっと黙って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.81,0:02:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You've kept the truth\Nfrom me all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:46.33,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 私は知りました
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:50.27,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お兄様がゼロだったのですね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Big brother, you were Zero{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}all along, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:51.08,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:53.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Why?! Were you doing it for my sake?{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}If that's the case, then l...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:56.42,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それは　私のためですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:58.84,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もしそうなら 私は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:01.29,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ふはははっお前のため？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,For your sake? I see my little\Nsister is as presumptuous as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:04.30,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,我が妹ながら図々しいことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:04.99,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:09.59,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,人からお恵みを頂くことが当たり前だと考えているのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's natural for people\Nto always help you out of pity?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:13.36,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,自らは手を汚さず　他人の行動だけを責める
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All you do is criticize the actions of others\Nwhile your own hands remain undirtied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:13.85,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:18.19,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前は俺が否定した古い貴族そのものだな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the very embodiment of\Nthe aristocracy which I have rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:20.30,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そん　な
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}You... don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:22.35,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,誰のためでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I do this for no one! It is for my\Nown benefit that I take the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:25.70,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺は　俺自身のために世界を手に入れる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:27.60,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前がシュナイゼルと手を組み
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you choose to ally yourself\Nwith Schneizel and stand in my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:31.42,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,我が覇道の前に立ちはだかるというのなら容赦はしない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.42,0:03:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice but\Nto crush you without mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:32.89,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,叩き潰すだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:34.32,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おにいさま
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,通信をきるルルーシュ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:40.99,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大丈夫か？ナナリー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Nunnally?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:43.28,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つらい思いをさせてしまったね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That must have\Nbeen hard for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:47.45,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,フレイヤの威力をみせれば　降伏してくれるとおもったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought showing him the power of the\NF.L.E.I.J.A. would lead him to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:49.09,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,シュナイゼル兄様
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Schneizel... Are the people\Nof Pendragon really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:53.13,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ペンドラゴンの人たちは本当に大丈夫なのですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:57.40,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,心配いらないよあらかじめ　避難誘導をすませたからね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You needn't worry. We gave warning\Nfor them to evacuate beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:01.25,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もちろん 被害が皆無とはいかないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the damage was significant,\Nbut we tried to minimize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:03.55,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,最小限にとどめたつもりだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:08.06,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも　次は人に　お兄様たちにつかうのでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,シュナイゼルの言葉をきいてうつむくコーネリア
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But, now... Now we'll have to use\Nthem on people. On big brother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:11.74,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,彼らが　世界平和の前に立ちはだかるのならば
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If they stand in the way\Nof world peace, we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:13.10,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,シュナイゼル兄様
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Schneizel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:17.29,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私に フレイヤの発射スイッチをいただけませんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you let me have the\NF.L.E.I.J.A. firing switch, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:21.69,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は戦うことも　守ることもできません
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't fight or protect\Nanything myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:25.88,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから　せめて　罪だけは背負いたいんです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, at the very least...\NI want this sin to be on my shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.70,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,兄上少しよろしいですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, may I have\Na word with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:32.52,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,くっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:35.86,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.！なぜナナリーのことがわからなかった？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,C.C., why didn't you\Nknow about Nunnally?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.78,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は神ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a god. I can't know about\Nanyone unconnected to Geass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:41.09,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ギアスによるつながりがない人間のことまでは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:43.24,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,くっシュナイゼルめ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Schneizel!\NYou kept the truth from me all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:45.71,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この事実を今までかくしておいたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:48.27,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,カードとして効果的につかうために
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you could play this card\Nwhen the time was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,チェスの駒をはらいおとすルルーシュ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:52.76,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ならば 貴様のカードの切り方は絶妙だったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, the way you shuffled\Nyour deck was extraordinary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:56.38,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こんなにも　こんなにも　ううっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So masterfully...\NSo masterfully!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:57.44,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,胸をおさえるルルーシュ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Lelouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュに近づき胸倉をつかみあげるスザク
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:01.21,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,戦略目的は変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Our strategic objective\Nremains unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:04.20,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ナナリーが生きていたからといって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't stop this just\Nbecause Nunnally is still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:05.63,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,立ち止まることはできない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:08.52,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何のためのゼロレクイエムだ？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of\Nthe Zero Requiem, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュを突き放します
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:12.08,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,約束を思い出せ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember your promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,部屋からでていくスザクをよびとめるC.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:13.82,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,スザク
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:20.31,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕は彼の剣だ彼の敵も弱さも僕が排除する
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I am his sword. I rid him of his\Nenemies and his own weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:23.51,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だからC.C. 君は盾になってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, C.C., you must\Nbecome his shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:26.57,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,守るのは君の役目だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Protecting him is your duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:28.58,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,勝手な言い分だな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's only what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:31.75,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュは 君の共犯者なんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lelouch is your accomplice, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:35.77,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,共犯者　か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My accomplice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,セシルさんとロイドさんとニーナ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:38.58,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ペンドラゴンでつかわれたフレイヤは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to the F.L.E.I.J.A.\Nused on the Tokyo settlement,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:40.70,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,トウキョウ租界のときにくらべて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the one used on Pendragon\Nhad ten times the effective range.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:42.74,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,効果範囲はおよそ10倍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:47.30,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,新規生産ではないとすると
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If they haven't manufactured\Na new model, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:49.98,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,リミッターを　はずした　？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They've removed\Nthe limiter from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.05,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やっぱり
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:55.02,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,効果範囲と起爆時間の制限をはずすなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Removing the effective range\Nand detonation time limiter...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:57.05,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,シュナイゼル殿下が
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Schneizel, how could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.40,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それがなにか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:02.43,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,で では ペンドラゴンの住民は　？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the people\Nof Pendragon were!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:03.96,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,消えてもらったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I made them vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:06.16,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その方が幸せじゃないのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Happier for them than a life\Nswearing loyalty to Lelouch, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:08.81,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュに忠誠を誓う人生よりは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:10.09,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しかし ナナリーには
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you told Nunnally...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:11.96,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘も方便だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies are expedient.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:15.95,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ナナリーがルルーシュに立ち向かうと決意してもらうには
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to tell Nunnally anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that would get in the way of\Nher opposition to Lelouch, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:19.02,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よけいな情報は　いれないほうがいいだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.64,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,兄上はそうやって人をあやつるのですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how you use\Npeople, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:25.49,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,コーネリア　人々の願いはなんだい？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Cornelia, what is it\Nthat people wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.40,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,飢餓や貧困
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Starvation and poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.12,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,差別 腐敗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Discrimination and corruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.28,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,戦争とテロリズム
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,War and terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:34.98,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,世界にあふれる問題をなくしたいと願いつつ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They wish for the problems\Nflooding the world to go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:38.07,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,人は絶望的なまでにわかりあえない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,People desperately cannot\Nunderstand each other. And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:39.02,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:41.81,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,理想としてはわかりますが 民間人を
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand your ideals,\Nbut to do this to the civilians!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:42.79,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,う～ん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:48.26,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,戦争を否定する民間人だって警察は頼りにするよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even civilians who have rejected war\Ndepend on the police, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:49.89,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,みんなわかっているんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone understands\Nthat crime cannot be stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:51.96,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,犯罪はとめられないと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:54.99,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,人それぞれの欲望は 否定できないと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,because people can't\Nhelp the desires they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:58.95,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だったら 心や主義主張はいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we don't need\Nto win hearts or use ideology.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:02.49,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,システムと力で 平和を実現すべきでは？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not bring peace to\Nthe world using a system backed by force?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:09.15,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,このダモクレスは　10日後に合集国中華の領空にはいり
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In 10 days, Damocles will enter the\Nairspace of the United States of China...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:11.16,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,第二次加速に移行する
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and then switch over\Nto secondary acceleration.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:14.88,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その後 地上300キロメートルまで上昇する予定だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, we're scheduled to ascend\Nto 300 kilometers above the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:18.81,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その位置から 戦争を行うすべての国にフレイヤを撃ちこむ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,From that position, we will hit every\Nwarmongering nation with F.L.E.I.J.A.s.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:20.17,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,待って下さい！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Shouldn't they be used to defeat\NLelouch?! This will devastate the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:22.38,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュを討つためだったのではなかったのですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:24.33,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これでは世界中が
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:27.06,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖で人を従えようというのですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to control\Npeople through fear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:29.63,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,平和というのは幻想だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace is an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.52,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,戦うことが人の歴史
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind's history is one of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:35.85,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,幻想を現実にするためには　しつけが必要では？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is not discipline what is needed\Nto make an illusion reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.27,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,人類を教育するつもりですか！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And you plan to teach that lesson\Nto the entire human race?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:41.56,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そのようなことは　神でなければ許されない！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Only God can get away\Nwith something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:43.21,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だったら 神になろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I shall become a God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:46.86,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,人々が　平和を私に望むのならば
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If that is what people want me\Nto become to give them peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:48.30,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:49.70,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,素晴らしい！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:53.02,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やっぱりあなたについてきて正解でした！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I was right\Nto come with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:56.21,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロのカオスをも凌駕する完璧な虚無
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Surpassing Zero's chaos to\Na state of perfect nothingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:57.92,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,多様なる変幻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,followed by a kaleidoscopic\Ntransformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:01.62,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,シュナイゼル殿下黒の騎士団と連絡がつきました
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Schneizel, we've made\Ncontact with the Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:04.54,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュを討つためならば　手を組むと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They say if you plan to kill Lelouch,\Nthey're willing to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:05.75,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:09.02,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュの暴虐を経験した民衆は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The masses who suffer Lelouch's\Ntyranny will have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:11.83,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よりましなアイデアにすがるしかないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but to cling to something\Nslightly better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:12.77,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そのために
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that's why you've let\NLelouch get away with this until now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:15.10,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュの行動をみすごしたというのですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:17.85,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もっとも被害の少ない方法だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the way to\Nminimize the damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:21.80,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,たとえ10億　20億の命がなくなったとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we lose 1 or 2 billion lives,\Nfor a permanent peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:23.28,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,恒久的な平和が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:24.31,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,違います！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!\NPeace given by force is no peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:26.66,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,強制的な平和など それは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,シュナイゼルが指で合図すると
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:37.96,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,悲しいねコーネリア
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You make me sad, Cornelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,手当をうけた咲世子さんは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.47,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,トウキョウ決戦のとき
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Schneizel had another escape plane as a\Ndecoy during the battle for Tokyo. And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:47.51,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,シュナイゼルは囮として　もう一機　脱出艇を
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:49.21,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:52.29,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,フレイヤで消失したのは囮のほうか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the plane destroyed by\Nthe F.L.E.I.J.A. was the decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:54.73,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ナナリー様を利用して
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to use Miss Nunnally\Nto control Master Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.15,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュ様をあやつろうなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:59.42,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,君は日本人だろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:08:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Japanese, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:02.52,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なぜ黒の騎士団ではなくルルーシュ様に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why come to Master Lelouch\Ninstead of the Black Knights?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:07.89,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士道に殉じるか 君も
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You devote yourself to\Nchivalry as well, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:11.15,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうかもしれませんね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュの部屋にC.C.がはいってきました
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:24.63,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よく仮面をかぶりつづけたな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed you maintained your mask,\Neven in front of Nunnally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:26.30,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ナナリーの前で
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:30.22,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いくつルートを探っても　答えは同じだったからな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what angle I attack the problem from,\Nthe answer is always the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:33.54,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あのときの結論にまちがいはないと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That the conclusion\NI made then wasn't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:36.89,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュもう十分じゃないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Lelouch, haven't you done enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.07,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おまえはよくやった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュの隣にすわるC.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:42.31,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おれが悪をなさねばならない理由はよくわかっているだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand why\NI'm doing this evil, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:45.23,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それに ダモクレスによる支配は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, under the rule of Damocles,\Npeople will become lifeless symbols.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:46.89,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,人を記号とするものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:50.22,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しかし ダモクレスにはナナリーがいる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But Nunnally is aboard Damocles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.78,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おまえは今までナナリーのために
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All you've done\Nhas been for her sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:57.29,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もう　特別扱いはできない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't treat her differently anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:59.85,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,消えていったあまたの命のためにも
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't stop now,\Nfor the sake of all those who have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:02.33,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おれたちは止まるわけにはいかないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.61,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだろう？C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, C.C.?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:12.45,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ　そうだなルルーシュ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You're right, Lelouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そのそばでナイトメアフレームをみつめるスザクの手にはアーサー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:33.07,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいの？いっしょに戦うなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you want\Nto be fighting with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:35.78,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ブリタニアを敵にすることになるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fighting against\NBritannia, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:37.85,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いまならさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:42.59,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いまならさ 君の気持ちも少しはわかる気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I understand\Nyour feelings just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:45.49,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,え　え～っと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.44,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どういたしまして
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:49.57,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんだそりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,黒の騎士団
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:59.89,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,神聖ブリタニア帝国は　帝都ペンドラゴンが消滅したため
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:12:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,With the destruction of Pendragon,\Nthe capital of the Holy Britannian Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.80,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,内政機能はまひしている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,their internal administration\Nhas been paralyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:06.29,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,各エリアの軍隊は　われわれ黒の騎士団と対峙しており
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,With them confronting the armies of\Nevery Area as well as the Black Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:07.70,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,へたには動けない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,they can't make any false moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:10.87,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つまり　こちらと戦えるルルーシュ軍は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, the only force Lelouch\Ncan send against us here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:12.99,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,日本を再占領した部隊のみ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is just the division he\Nbrought to reoccupy Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:16.90,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しかし このパワーバランスはいつくずれてもおかしくありません
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this balance of\Npower can collapse at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:19.26,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,被害を最小限にとどめるには
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To minimize damage,\Nthe time to confront him is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.47,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,決戦のタイミングは今しか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:24.48,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,シュナイゼルがわれわれに合流した以上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Schneizel has joined up with us,\Nour forces are evenly matched.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:26.58,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,彼我の戦力は伯仲している
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:29.85,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,フレイヤをつかったダモクレスを認める気はないが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't intend to approve of\NDamocles's use of F.L.E.I.J.A. weaponry,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:32.90,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この場は世界がまとまることを優先したい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but uniting the world has priority here.\NThis battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:34.26,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この戦いが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:38.26,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この戦いこそが世界をかけた決戦となる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その言葉をひきつぐルルーシュ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This battle is a showdown\Nwith control of the world at stake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:40.69,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,シュナイゼルと黒の騎士団を倒せば
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If we defeat Schneizel and the Black Knights,\Nthen there will be none left to stand in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:43.59,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,わが覇道をはばむものは一掃される
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:47.79,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,世界は ブリタニア皇帝唯一ルルーシュによって破壊され
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The world shall be destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and then recreated by Lelouch,\Nthe one, true emperor of Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:50.26,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しかるのちに創造されるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:54.16,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,打ち砕くのだ！敵を！シュナイゼルを！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Smash them! Smash Schneizel!\NSmash the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:56.55,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,天空要塞ダモクレスを！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Smash the sky fortress Damocles!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:58.54,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おそれることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We have nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:01.65,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,未来は　我が名とともにあり！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is the future of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:04.10,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オール　ハイル　ルルーシュ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All hail Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,シュナイゼル
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:09.51,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュは　世界のすべてに悪意をふりまく存在だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Lelouch spreads malice{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}over the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:12.40,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,平和の敵はこの地で討たねばならない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}As the enemy of peace,{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}he must be wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:14.13,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,過去のしがらみは捨て
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I want us and the Black Knights to throw off\Nthe fetters of the past and join forces here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:16.06,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私たちも　黒の騎士団も
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:18.87,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここはともに手をたずさえたい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:21.35,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,世界中の人々が待っている
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of the world are waiting!\NFor our song of victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.61,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私たちの凱歌を
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:26.29,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そして願わくば
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And I pray that this is the last war\Nthat mankind need ever fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:30.83,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これが人類にとって　最後の戦争であることを祈りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.40,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lelouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,学校でとった写真をみつめるアーニャ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:39.38,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ふたりとも 記録にしてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make both of you\Ninto recordings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:41.71,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アーニャは大丈夫なのですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,シュナイゼルたちの部屋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure\NAnya will be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:44.73,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下は記憶を戻すとおっしゃられましたが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you promised to restore\Nher memory, Your Highness, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:48.67,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今は少しでも戦力が必要だよだから
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We need every bit of\Nbattle strength we have. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そこへルルーシュから通信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:52.33,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ほ～うオープンチャンネルで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? On an open channel, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:55.27,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごきげんようシュナイゼル
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}You look well, Schneizel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:14:00.70,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュ降伏するなら今のうちだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lelouch, if you're going\Nto surrender, now is the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.47,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こちらには　フレイヤの用意がある
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We have F.L.E.I.J.A.s here,\Nready to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:04.83,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,フレイヤ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}F.L.E.I.J.A.s? I wonder if{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}you'd dare to fire them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:06.89,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,撃てるかな？あなたに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:11.54,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,わが旗艦アヴァロンには各合衆国の代表方がおられるが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Considering I have the U.F.N.{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}representatives aboard the Avalon with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:13.72,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,人質をたてとする気か
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's hiding behind\Nthe hostages?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:17.09,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そこまでやるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\Nhe'd go this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:18.35,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,シュナイゼル
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I know they're not directly{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}related to you, Schneizel, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:21.68,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたにとっては関係のない人たちではあるが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:23.38,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだねルルーシュ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, Lelouch. They're a\Nsmall price to pay for world peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.43,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,世界の平和とわずかな命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:26.65,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,撃つなよシュナイゼル！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Don't shoot, Schneizel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,と　わりこむシンクー（天子?命）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:31.57,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,各合衆国では代表代行が選出されたとききましたが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the U.F.N. members have\Nelected substitute representatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:33.69,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いざというときの覚悟はある
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}We're ready for the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:37.66,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しかしだからといって無駄にしていい命など存在しない！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}But that doesn't mean their{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}lives are to be thrown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:39.16,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ははははっ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:41.27,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,リ　シンクー
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:44.39,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,わが方の戦力は　このダモクレス以外は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Li Xing-ke, the only power we have aside\Nfrom Damocles is a single Mordred.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:46.16,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,モルドレッド一機のみ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:48.02,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,フレイヤをつかわないのであれば
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're not to use the F.L.E.I.J.A.s, I'd like\Nto take command of all our forces, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:51.40,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この場は全体の指揮権を私に預けてほしいが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:52.87,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,相手はルルーシュだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}We're facing Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:54.87,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,心配はいらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.34,0:15:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Have no fear. I've never lost to Lelouch even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:55.87,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私はね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:58.82,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一度だってルルーシュに負けたことはないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:00.69,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,わかった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:03.89,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,シェンフーをだす
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Deploy the Shen Hu. Transmit the\Ncommand structure to all forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.14,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,全軍に指揮系統を伝達してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.02,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:09.36,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まずは手合わせといきましょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Then shall we have at each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:10.36,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,通信を切ります
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:13.83,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,カノン君のよみどおりに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kannon, just as you predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:17.21,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はいこれで黒の騎士団は　殿下の手足です
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Now the Black Knights are yours to command.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:20.44,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ふっ全軍にパターンシグマを伝えて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Transmit pattern Sigma to all forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:26.46,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,敵軍　航空部隊を広範囲に展開させようとしています
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy forces deploying into\Na wide-field aerial formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:28.19,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,通常戦闘でくるか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming at me with\Nconventional tactics? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:29.32,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:32.43,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,左翼をのばせ半月羅漢の陣を敷く
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Stretch our left wing!\NAssume Half-Moon Arhat formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:34.08,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,イエス　ユア　マジェスティ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:38.88,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,敵本陣が手薄ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's main unit\Nis undermanned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:40.55,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ジノの部隊は前進
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Have Gino's unit advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:43.06,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,敵左翼がのびる先をおさえて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep the enemy's left wing\Nfrom extending!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:44.84,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,イエス　ユア　ハイネス
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:50.17,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,牽制か　こちらの左翼を後退させろ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Checking my move, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Move our left wing back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:52.17,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それでは陣形がくずれます
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That will break our formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:52.84,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:56.76,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ジノ進撃を停止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Gino, halt your advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:59.55,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なぜです？陣形の崩れた今こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Why? We should strike now{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}while their formation is breaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.15,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,誘いの隙だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's baiting us with an opening.\NI'm not taking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.43,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,のることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:04.08,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つられないか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.87,0:16:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not falling for it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:07.18,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,陣立てを北斗七星陣に変更
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch main battle plan\Nto Big Dipper formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.59,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,６番隊はアーニャを中心に北東へ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 6, follow Anya and move to the\Nnortheast, elevation 40 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:13.90,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,仰角40度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:17.58,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,砲撃部隊　対空戦闘準備
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bombardment unit,\Nprep for anti-air combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:20.63,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アーニャそこで停止２００ｍ上昇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Anya, stop there\Nand climb 200 meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.62,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんだよ！全然戦いにならねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell!\NNobody's fighting at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:28.86,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,違う達人同士の戦いが一瞬で決まるように
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong. A battle between\Ntwo masters is decided in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:31.98,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,みえない攻撃が2人の間を行きかっている
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,An invisible battle is now raging\Nbetween the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:38.53,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,急がないと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry.\NThe battle's already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:41.09,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もう戦闘ははじまっているのに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:44.76,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,囲まれつつあります！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They're surrounding us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:46.59,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちっ反撃だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:49.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,スザクのランスロットを全面に押し立てろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Counterattack! Reinforce the\Nfront line with Suzaku's Lancelot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:50.76,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,第４速度でいい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold at combat speed 4!\NSend Ward's unit out as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.81,0:16:52.04,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ウォード隊も続け！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.79,0:16:54.67,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,かわらないねルルーシュ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed, Lelouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:57.77,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,君は防御よりも攻撃が好きだった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You like to attack\Nmore than defend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:16:59.85,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だからこそのわずかな隙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Which leaves me a small\Nwindow of opportunity. Xing-ke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:01.24,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,シンクー？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.34,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,シンクー突撃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:04.67,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,われらの技量までおり込み済みか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Heh... He's already incorporated{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}our skills into his tactics, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:06.75,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,敵左翼　前進してきます
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy left wing, advancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:11.54,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ひるむな!陛下のご期待にこたえるのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Give no quarter! Live up to His\NMajesty's confidence in us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:18.93,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュを倒せば すべておわれる！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can defeat Lelouch, {\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}this all will end!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:26.26,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここを破って　混戦にもちこめば！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If we break the line here and\Nturn this into a free-for-all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:33.67,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うっ突破される
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They're breaking through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.75,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ひきちぎられるか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're being cut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:38.49,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,スザクくんをもどしますか？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I recall Suzaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:41.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいや それがシュナイゼルの狙いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's what Schneizel wants us to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:43.84,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,戦線をさげよ陣形をたてなおす
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw the battle line!\NRegroup our forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:46.03,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,敵艦隊　後退していきます
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy fleet falling back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:50.10,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この機をのがすな！追撃！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Don't lose this chance! Press the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:57.59,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,紅蓮は先行しすぎだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:18:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Guren, you're too far out! Match pace{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}with us and we'll surround them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:17:59.26,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,足並みをそろえて包囲しろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.29,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,わかっています！でも
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.18,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あせるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:05.85,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,前衛部隊を砕けばアヴァロンは孤立する
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be in a rush! If we defeat their\Nvanguard, the Avalon will be left isolated!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:10.42,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ドレッドノート撃沈！突破されます！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreadnought, destroyed! They're breaking through!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:11.69,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,黒の騎士団
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the Black Knights are this\Nstrong an enemy, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:14.77,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,敵にまわすとこれほどやっかいな相手だったか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:17.30,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しかし　我が軍の兵は　?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,However, as for my own troops...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:19.74,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝陛下のために～！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,For His Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:27.44,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哀れだなギアスによって操られている兵士とは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's heartbreaking. Seeing soldiers\Ncontrolled by Geass. Therefore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:28.88,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゆえに！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:33.93,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今かな両翼をくだこう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I suppose now is the time.{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Smash both wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:36.21,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,艦首拡散ハドロン重砲セット！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bow-mounted hadron\Nscatter cannon, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:38.28,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,7番隊　射角外へ移動！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Move squad 7 out of the firing angle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:40.03,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゲフィオンコントロール　同調よし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gefjun control, synched.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:41.04,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いけます
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:43.64,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,敵軍両翼にむけ　発射！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Target both enemy wings.\NFire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:49.51,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロみんなの力をあわせれば
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Zero, with everyone joined together,{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}we can defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:50.92,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,君を倒せる！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:56.49,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュは黒の騎士団を過小評価していたようですね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Lelouch underestimated\Nthe Black Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:57.48,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とディートハルト
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.43,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああさすがだな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Lelouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I'm impressed.\NYou've forced me to use this plan, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:01.31,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この策を使わせるとは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:08.18,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しまった！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:10.03,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,エネルギー反応 下からです
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Energy reaction, right below us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:10.68,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何っ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:12.86,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まさかこのタイミングで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Impossible...\NHe timed this to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:17.59,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,全軍　輻射障壁を展開しろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}All forces!{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Raise radiant shields!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゼロ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:29.98,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,最初にゼロ ルルーシュを認めてしまったのは俺だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one who first recognized\NZero's... Lelouch's leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:32.42,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから俺には責任がある
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why this is my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:36.19,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しかし 新しい命は巻き込みたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want\Na new life caught up in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:38.76,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,勝手なお願いなのはわかっている
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this is a selfish\Nrequest I'm making,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:42.86,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 君にはこの蓬莱島に残ってほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but I want you stay\Nhere on Horai Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:46.78,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,扇さん！応答してください！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Ohgi, please respond!{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Minami! Rakshata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:48.96,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,南さん！ラクシャータさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:53.58,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そ そんな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:56.41,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しかし　サクラダイトをつかって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He used the sakuradite\Nin the mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:20:01.02,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これでは　ルルーシュの地上部隊も全滅だね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This has destroyed Lelouch's\Nground forces as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:02.78,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うかつ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:06.09,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュの基本戦術ではあったが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Lelouch's basic tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:08.74,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,味方を犠牲にすることが前提とは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But how can he sacrifice\Nhis own forces?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:13.38,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これで　敵の戦力は絞られた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This has left the enemy's strength nearly\Ndepleted. That leaves Damocles...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:14.88,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,後はダモクレスを
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:16.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,たたくだけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For us to hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:21.63,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,残念だが チェックをかけられたのは君たちの方だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it's you who\Nhave been checked here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:24.62,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ナナリー 照準は合わせてある
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Nunnally, targeting is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:26.62,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,黒の騎士団がついえた今
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Now that the Black Knights have been{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}smashed, we must use F.L.E.I.J.A.'s power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:28.28,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,フレイヤという力で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:30.17,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,は はい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.84,0:20:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:36.98,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お兄様の罪は　私が討ちます
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,With this act, I will wipe away\Nbig brother's sins!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.41,0:20:40.94,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,きました！フレイヤです！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Incoming! It's a F.L.E.I.J.A.!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.63,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここで撃ってきたか第三特装師団
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, here's where he's fired it.\NSpecial equipment division 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:45.41,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,イエス　ユア　マジェスティ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Yes, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:47.51,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,無駄だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:52.12,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,このフレイヤは　ダモクレスから射出されたときには臨界状態にある
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless. The F.L.E.I.J.A. went critical\Nthe moment it was fired from Damocles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.64,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アヴァロンはこのまま後退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:21:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Avalon will continue to fall back.\NAll forces, charge at Damocles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:21:00.33,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,各部隊はダモクレスにに突撃しフレイヤを撃たせ続けろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Make them keep firing F.L.E.I.J.A. s\Nuntil they exhaust their stock!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:01.84,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,弾切れにおいこむんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:00:00.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,扇さんによびかける玉城とカレン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.57,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,扇！扇！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Ohgi! Ohgi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.51,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,扇さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Ohgi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:15.15,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,死んだふりしてる場合か！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Is this any time{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}to be playing dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:18.58,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ま まさか おまえたち　盾になって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I... I don't believe it.{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}You two shielded us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:22.04,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,へへっブリッジぐらいしか守れなかったけどよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.86,0:21:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We were only able to\Nprotect the bridge, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.27,0:21:24.56,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まあとは自力でなんとかしてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on your own now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:26.41,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,行くぞ！カレン！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:29.19,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何よえらそうに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Oh please, look who's{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}giving orders now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:32.70,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちっ富士の作戦を使ってしまった以上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Now that I've used the Fuji plan,{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I calculate his remaining F.L.E.I.J.A.s...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.86,0:21:35.02,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,フレイヤの残弾から計算すると
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:37.00,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こちらが一手不利になる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}put me at a one-move{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.20,0:21:40.17,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とすると ニーナを頼りにするしかないが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Meaning I have to{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}depend on Nina now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.39,0:21:41.72,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あてにできるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Can she do it?{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}I know she hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:43.96,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺を憎んでいるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:47.79,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ユフィのかたき　ゼロであった俺を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Hates me for being Zero,{\r}\N{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}Euphy's murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:51.10,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しかし シュナイゼルを倒すためには
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\fs24}{\fnArial}But, to defeat Schneizel...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:55.78,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュ もし私を倒そうと考えているのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Lelouch, if you're thinking\Nthat you can defeat me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:21:57.68,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,君はそこまでだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you've reached\Nthe end of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:22:02.04,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,仮面を使いこなせない人間に　勝利はない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.26,0:22:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For a man who has not mastered\Nthe use of a mask can never prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.21,0:22:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dakuse wa oni\NThis corrupt world is filled with demons
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Seigi wa nanzo to\NWhat is justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tou mae ni aragae yo\NResist, don't just question
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.59,0:22:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Akutoku no hana\NThe flower of evil
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Gizen no yume\NDreams of hypocrisy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.49,0:22:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mishi me niwa me wo sashi\NGive your gaze to the eyes that see them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.09,0:22:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sei mo ja mo wakatareru koto nashi\NThe line between right and wrong cannot be known
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.50,0:22:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari wa tae taiji no you ni\NLight is gone, and you slumber
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi wa nemuru yami no shikyuu\NLike an unborn child in the womb of darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kodoku koso itooshii\NIsolation is what you love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-itsu no mikata to naru darou\NIt will probably be your only ally
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitori hitori chishio ni mamire\NOne by one, stained with the tide of blood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kono jidai ni umare ochita\NYou were born into this era
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Erabareshi oujira yo\NOh, chosen princes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.32,0:22:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatakai koso shukuen\NBattle shall be your banquet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Aa ware wa uruwashii zenchi\NOh, I am graceful omniscience
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.63,0:23:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai no haha\NThe loving mother
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.43,0:23:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi wo umu\NWho bore you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.34,0:23:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kono chichi ni hagukumishi mono wa\NThe ones who were raised on my breast
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Jigoku no harakara\NAre your brethren in hell
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.94,0:23:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mokushi no in\NThe mark of apocalypse
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.75,0:23:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinri wa nanzo to\NWhat is truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.35,0:23:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirimosezu uzumoreshi intoku no tane\NA seed of secrecy buried where no one knows
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.32,0:23:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Moroha no ken\NA double-edged sword
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.15,0:23:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuku ha niwa ha wo muke\NTurn its blade upon the unsheathed blade
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.82,0:23:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mamorubeki mono dake wo shinjite\NBelieve only in what you must protect
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Aru ga mama ni kimi wa\NAnd in your own way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.23,0:23:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi wo hanate\NYou'll set yourself free
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:39.45,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オレとスザク二人が手を組めば出来ないことは無い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.79,0:23:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzaku and me. Together,\Nthere's nothing we can't accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:40.98,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そのはずだった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.03,0:23:46.21,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,しかしフレイヤが支配する戦場にもはや戦術は通用しないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.26,0:23:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought,\Nbut now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.00,0:23:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The fearsomeness of Schneizel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.97,0:23:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, it's his\Nlack of personal desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.42,0:23:49.63,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,最後の鍵は？そのカードは？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.11,0:23:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of strategy will come from\Na man who knows about Geass,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,possesses F.L.E.I.J.A.,\Nand is determined to achieve his goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.38,0:23:53.46,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルルーシュだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.94,0:23:55.72,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今週も楽しんでくれてありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.14,0:23:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can no tactic work now on a\Nbattlefield dominated by F.L.E.I.J.A.?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.11,0:23:59.84,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いつも応援してくれているみんなにご覧のプレゼントを送る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.62,0:24:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one last gamble to try,\None final card to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.21,0:24:02.35,cn.sub-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こちらのケータイサイトから応募してほしい
